                                    "content": "<ul class='list-disc pl-6 space-y-1'><li><strong>Jiva</strong> - Soul or living being (Consciousness)</li><li><strong>Ajiva</strong> - Non-living substances</li></ul>"
                                },
                                {
                                    "header": "Heya - Those to be avoided",
                                    "content": "<ul class='list-disc pl-6 space-y-1'><li><strong>√Ñsrav</strong> - Influx of karma</li><li><strong>Bandha</strong> - Bondage of karma</li><li><strong>P√§p</strong> - Sin</li></ul>"
                                },
                                {
                                    "header": "Up√§deya - Those to be adopted",
                                    "content": "<ul class='list-disc pl-6 space-y-1'><li><strong>Punya</strong> - Virtue</li><li><strong>Samvar</strong> - Stoppage of the influx of karma</li><li><strong>Nirjar√§</strong> - Partial eradication of accumulated karma</li><li><strong>Moksh</strong> - Total liberation from karma</li></ul>"
